16
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,260
Tired?

17
00:01:02,260 --> 00:01:06,300
Yeah. I was on the phone with
a certain someone all night.

18
00:01:06,300 --> 00:01:07,330
A certain someone?

19
00:01:07,330 --> 00:01:11,800
When we finished it was an hour
too early to leave for school.

20
00:01:11,800 --> 00:01:15,040
Why not sleep during class?
That's what I do.

21
00:01:15,810 --> 00:01:20,440
A teacher sleeping in class?
Oh, maybe I should give a test.

22
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:24,350
That would be horrible!

23
