39
00:02:25,410 --> 00:02:29,680
- Want to go?
- Huh?

40
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,710
Do you want to go with me?

41
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:34,500
Can you go out with your teacher?

42
00:02:35,580 --> 00:02:38,950
