him before he was a teacher.

66
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:24,110
No, I didn't.

67
00:04:24,110 --> 00:04:26,040
But you were with him
until morning.

68
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:29,800
- Nothing happened though.
- Whatever.

69
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:33,980
It's amazing though, isn't it?

70
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:37,420
