71
00:04:37,420 --> 00:04:40,320
- Really?
- Like you didn't know.

72
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:42,930
I can't believe you got him.

73
00:04:42,930 --> 00:04:46,100
Like I said, I didn't "get him".

74
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:49,570
I guess you're kinda cute.
If you look real close.

75
00:04:49,570 --> 00:04:52,590
No, I'm not. I'm plain.

76
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:57,140
You're the one who has your boyfriend
waiting outside the gates everyday.

77
00:04:57,140 --> 00:04:58,900
I didn't tell him to.

78
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:02,600
He's really cool.

79
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:05,410
He's just after money.

80
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:10,990
Well, the teacher's just
pitying me.

81
00:05:10,990 --> 00:05:13,320
How?

82
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:16,390
- Do you really want to know?
- Whatever.

83
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:20,130
