while solving this problem.

85
00:06:05,900 --> 00:06:07,900
Hina!

86
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:13,180
No way!

87
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:15,690
- Poor guy!
- Wait!

88
00:06:15,690 --> 00:06:17,600
Hey!

89
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:30,270
Everybody, go back
to your seats.

90
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:37,270
This isn't a joke! Get off me!

91
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:39,630
Come on! Let go!

92
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:42,040
Let go!

93
00:06:44,900 --> 00:06:49,000
