anything bad.

124
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:55,700
Just tell her the truth right away.

125
00:08:55,700 --> 00:08:59,800
It's not just for her.
It's for you, too.

126
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:01,500
I understand what you're saying.

127
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:04,620
