146
00:10:11,260 --> 00:10:13,070
Fine.

147
00:10:13,070 --> 00:10:15,220
I'll get you some medicine.

148
00:10:15,220 --> 00:10:18,090
I'm okay.

149
00:10:19,330 --> 00:10:22,200
I'll be going now.

150
00:10:48,590 --> 00:10:51,560
Why don't you wait outside
of her house?

151
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:56,090
That sounds like something
a stalker would do.

152
00:10:56,090 --> 00:10:59,500
- It's hard to draw the line.
- Gotcha.

153
00:10:59,500 --> 00:11:02,660
Thanks to you, the cops gave
me a good beating.

154
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:04,640
