155
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,800
Maybe so.

156
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:11,180
Did you...

157
00:11:11,180 --> 00:11:14,200
Did you have a bad upbringing?

158
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:18,300
Abusive childhood?

159
00:11:21,290 --> 00:11:25,700
Perhaps you're bitter towards
your mother,

160
00:11:25,700 --> 00:11:28,330
and now you take it out
on women?

161
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:37,110
I'm sorry, but those excuses
are obsolete.

162
00:11:37,110 --> 00:11:40,410
It's not like that anymore.

163
00:11:40,410 --> 00:11:42,200
Why then?

164
00:11:43,350 --> 00:11:46,720
I guess I have no reason.

165
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,990
Does that annoy you?

166
00:11:48,990 --> 00:11:52,190
Come on, keep trying
to stop me.

167
00:11:52,190 --> 00:11:55,490
I told you I enjoyed your
determination.

168
00:11:58,660 --> 00:12:03,100
I'll leave you with a hint.

169
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:06,450
Teachers can't beat me
and neither can policemen.

170
00:12:08,340 --> 00:12:12,440
