176
00:12:49,850 --> 00:12:52,680
Can't sleep again?

177
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:58,390
Yeah. Maybe because I slept
in class today.

178
00:12:58,390 --> 00:13:01,120
You were sound asleep.

179
00:13:02,700 --> 00:13:08,600
About the weekend, it looks
like it's gonna rain.

180
00:13:09,900 --> 00:13:12,000
